title: Fruit Pochette -Shippujinrai
description:
For any of you Babymetal fans looking to journey a little further I present 

Fruit Pochette- This album has me right now and it only took 2 spins. The girls need a little more power in their vocals but as a unit these songs are pretty incredible and introduce a unique style.

I included their 1 video for Parasite.. 

Hope you enjoy and feel free to leave a comment if you like them
